<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Lucky Stone</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/</link><description>Recent content on Lucky Stone</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://luckystonetw.com/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>風象星座能量解析：雙子天秤水瓶的風之性格與守護水晶</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E9%A2%A8%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9B%99%E5%AD%90%E5%A4%A9%E7%A7%A4%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E4%B9%8B%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E9%A2%A8%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9B%99%E5%AD%90%E5%A4%A9%E7%A7%A4%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E4%B9%8B%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;風有很多種吹拂的方式——有的是春天的穿堂風，在每扇窗之間穿梭，帶來各個房間的消息；有的是傍晚的微風，溫柔地拂過水面，讓一切歸於和諧的漣漪；有的是高空的氣流，看不見摸不著，卻悄悄改變了整片天空的走向。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>12星座守護水晶完整對照表：找到你的命定之石</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/12%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E5%B0%8D%E7%85%A7%E8%A1%A8%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BD%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%8B%E7%9F%B3/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/12%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E5%B0%8D%E7%85%A7%E8%A1%A8%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BD%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%8B%E7%9F%B3/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;每個星座都有屬於自己的能量頻率，而在礦物的世界裡，也有一顆石頭正靜靜等著與你共振。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>水象星座能量解析：巨蟹天蠍雙魚的深海性格與守護水晶</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E6%B0%B4%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E5%B7%A8%E8%9F%B9%E5%A4%A9%E8%A0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B1%E6%B5%B7%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E6%B0%B4%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E5%B7%A8%E8%9F%B9%E5%A4%A9%E8%A0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B1%E6%B5%B7%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;水有很多種存在的方式——有的是溫暖的泉眼，從地底源源不絕地湧出，滋養著身邊的每一寸土地；有的是深不見底的海溝，表面看似平靜，底下卻藏著驚人的壓力與暗流；有的是無邊際的薄霧，瀰漫在空氣中，觸碰不到卻無處不在。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>火象星座能量解析：牡羊獅子射手的火焰性格與守護水晶</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%81%AB%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%89%A1%E7%BE%8A%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%81%AB%E7%84%B0%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%81%AB%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%89%A1%E7%BE%8A%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%81%AB%E7%84%B0%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;火焰有很多種燃燒的方式——有的像剛擦亮的火柴，瞬間點燃整片黑暗；有的像壁爐裡的炭火，持續散發溫暖的光芒；有的像營火的火星，隨風飄散到意想不到的遠方。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>牡羊座守護水晶完整指南：海藍寶與紅碧玉的能量搭配</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%89%A1%E7%BE%8A%E5%BA%A7%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E8%97%8D%E5%AF%B6%E8%88%87%E7%B4%85%E7%A2%A7%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%84%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E6%90%AD%E9%85%8D/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%89%A1%E7%BE%8A%E5%BA%A7%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E8%97%8D%E5%AF%B6%E8%88%87%E7%B4%85%E7%A2%A7%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%84%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E6%90%AD%E9%85%8D/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;牡羊座的能量像一把剛點燃的火焰——燃燒得又快又烈，照亮了整個房間，卻也偶爾不小心燙到身邊的人。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>處女座守護水晶完整指南：粉水晶與藍紋瑪瑙的能量搭配</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3%E5%BA%A7%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E7%B2%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%88%87%E8%97%8D%E7%B4%8B%E7%91%AA%E7%91%99%E7%9A%84%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E6%90%AD%E9%85%8D/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3%E5%BA%A7%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E7%B2%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%88%87%E8%97%8D%E7%B4%8B%E7%91%AA%E7%91%99%E7%9A%84%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E6%90%AD%E9%85%8D/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;處女座的內心住著一把精密的量尺，不斷測量著世界與自己之間的距離——哪裡還不夠好，哪裡還可以更好。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>土象星座能量解析：金牛處女摩羯的大地性格與守護水晶</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E5%9C%9F%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%87%91%E7%89%9B%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3%E6%91%A9%E7%BE%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E5%9C%9F%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%87%91%E7%89%9B%E8%99%95%E5%A5%B3%E6%91%A9%E7%BE%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;大地有很多種存在的方式——有的是春天的沃土，溫暖而肥沃，萬物都想在這裡扎根；有的是精心打理的花園，每一寸都被仔細安排，沒有一片葉子是多餘的；有的是高聳入雲的山岩，歷經風霜卻紋風不動，頂端的風景只屬於願意攀登的人。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶 x 眉心輪 &amp; 頂輪：一顆石頭，同時打開兩個靈性能量中心</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E8%BC%AA%E8%88%87%E9%A0%82%E8%BC%AA%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E8%BC%AA%E8%88%87%E9%A0%82%E8%BC%AA%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;大多數水晶只對應一個脈輪。紫水晶不一樣——它同時連結眉心輪和頂輪，也就是七脈輪體系裡最頂端的兩個能量中心。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶功效完整解析：靈性修行入門首選</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A5%E9%96%80%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A5%E9%96%80%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;在水晶店走了一圈，最後手裡還是捧著一顆紫水晶——你不孤單，幾乎每個人的起點都在這裡。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶怎麼用？冥想、助眠、空間淨化實戰完整指南</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E7%94%A8%E5%86%A5%E6%83%B3%E5%8A%A9%E7%9C%A0%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E7%94%A8%E5%86%A5%E6%83%B3%E5%8A%A9%E7%9C%A0%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;買了紫水晶，然後呢？&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶星座配對：雙魚、水瓶、射手為什麼特別有緣？</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A3/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;同樣一顆紫水晶，有人戴了感覺渾身舒暢，有人帶了幾個月幾乎沒感覺。這不全然是「信不信的問題」——星座跟水晶的共振確實有差。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶淨化方法完整指南：月光浴、煙燻、聲音療癒怎麼選？</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E6%9C%88%E5%85%89%E6%B5%B4%E7%85%99%E7%87%BB%E8%81%B2%E9%9F%B3%E7%99%82%E7%99%92%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E9%81%B8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E6%9C%88%E5%85%89%E6%B5%B4%E7%85%99%E7%87%BB%E8%81%B2%E9%9F%B3%E7%99%82%E7%99%92%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E9%81%B8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;水晶需要淨化——這件事很多人知道，但真正做到的不多。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>揭開誕生石的神奇面紗：揭開每顆寶石背後隱藏的意義和個性</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E6%8F%AD%E9%96%8B%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F%E7%9F%B3%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E9%9D%A2%E7%B4%97%E6%8F%AD%E9%96%8B%E6%AF%8F%E9%A1%86%E5%AF%B6%E7%9F%B3%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E9%9A%B1%E8%97%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E5%92%8C%E5%80%8B%E6%80%A7/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Jun 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E6%8F%AD%E9%96%8B%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F%E7%9F%B3%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E9%9D%A2%E7%B4%97%E6%8F%AD%E9%96%8B%E6%AF%8F%E9%A1%86%E5%AF%B6%E7%9F%B3%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E9%9A%B1%E8%97%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E5%92%8C%E5%80%8B%E6%80%A7/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;在星座學中，每個人的生日都與特定的寶石相關聯。這些寶石被稱為「誕生石」，據說具有特殊的意義和能量。讓我們釋放宇宙能量，發揮誕生石在你生活中的個人意義&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>渣女星座大解析：最毒舌、狡猾心機的星座</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E6%B8%A3%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%A7%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%9012%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%80%E5%85%B7%E6%AF%92%E8%88%8C%E7%8B%A1%E7%8C%BE%E5%BF%83%E6%A9%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%B3%E7%A5%9E%E5%80%91/</link><pubDate>Tue, 13 Jun 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E6%B8%A3%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%A7%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%9012%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%80%E5%85%B7%E6%AF%92%E8%88%